snippet.title: “EDENS ZERO”  Game Project Teaser
snippet.description:
Get ready for 2 exciting games in the making based on the manga “EDENS ZERO” by Hiro Mashima originally serialized in the weekly SHONEN MAGAZINE published by KODANSHA Ltd.  

Console : 3D Action RPG
Mobile : Top-down action RPG

*Game screen is under development.

Official Website  https://edens-zero.net/
